  Locus:
    Page: 79
    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Death
---
Death is not to be feared. It is a friend.No man dies before his hour. The
timeyou leave behind was no more yoursthan that which was before your
birthand concerneth you no more. Makeroom for others as others have done
foryou. Like a full-fed guest, depart torest.
